24/03/2003
TIRANA, Albania -- Prime Minister Fatos Nano ordered on Friday (21 March) establishment of a commission to monitor domestic oil prices, in an effort to avert hikes by speculators in response to the Iraq war. 
Petrol prices have surged by 38 per cent over the last three weeks. 
(Koha Jone - 24/03/03, Shekulli - 21/03/03)
